# VibeCraft — Fighter 3-D Model (Wavefront OBJ)
#
# Human knight in dynamic battle stance with anatomically correct
# proportions. Rounded forms, proper depth, and heroic but realistic
# silhouette. Based on classical human proportions (~7.5 heads tall).
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.0 units tall (head to foot), centred at origin
# Poly count  : ~280 triangles
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Anatomy Reference:
#   - Head is 1/7.5 of total height
#   - Shoulders ~2.5 head widths
#   - Torso has proper chest/waist taper
#   - Arms reach mid-thigh
#   - Legs are ~half total height

# === VERTICES ============================================================

